Be sure to edit the Makefile to specify where the 
various include files and libraries are.

This package requires xml++, boost's regex, and mysql++

Be sure to state the location for these packages (and mysql.h) in the
src/Makefile file.  Note that the plugins in the Plugin directory may also
need to have their Makefile modified, as well.

to create deaf:
   % make deaf

to create libDEAF.so
   % make libDEAF.so

to build standard set of plugins:
   % make plugins

to install deaf, libDEAF.so, include files and the standard set of plugins:
   % make install

to clean (everything, including standard set of plugins)
   % make clean

to uninstall (everything, including standard set of plugins)
   % make remove
